articles.title: 7 pathogens that have high chances of sparking a pandemic in 2024 as per WHO - Business Insider India
articles.description: ​The World Health Organisation recently released an updated list of pathogens that could trigger the next pandemic.​
articles.content: While the number of pathogens has grown to more than 30, there are 7 priority pathogens in particular that have high chances of causing Public Health Emergencies of International Concern.
